title: Jump pro - Black - Recycled black waterproof ski trousers  - Molo
meta_description: Jump Pro is a pair of functional, waterproof black pull on trousers that are particularly well suited as ski trousers because they are very durable. Because they are breathable and insulated, Jump Pro trousers are perfect for extremely cold days but also ordinary winter days. The high level of breathability helps regulate a child's body temperature so they do not become too cold or over heated. On warmer winter days, a child can wear the trousers with a thin under layer, but on extremely cold days, you can add an extra layer underneath. Jump Pro is also a good choice for less active moments. The trousers' outer fabric is made of 45% recycled nylon made from waste, while the lining and inner lining is 100% recycled. The trousers have a snap and zip closure at the waist, side pockets, adjustable leg openings with snow flaps and extra reinforcement at the inner legs. The trousers are constructed in waterproof, windproof and breathable materials. This product has a water resistant, PFC-free surface treatment (Does not contain, e.g. PFOS, PFOA, etc).
